metadata.name: Zaza the Elf
metadata.description: Elf Zaza is the Alchemist who weaves priceless jewels into existence. An epic story journey combining great NFT art, a Virtual Reality Game and two Fantasy/Action-Adventure Films. The Shaman’s Pack is a collection of Magic Mushroom Sacraments offered by the Shaman to the explorers who travels to Elfstan or the Elfverse seeking precious. The explorer consumes the Mushrooms….mysterious portals.
